    "bio": "<strong>Cameron Rumford</strong> is a Los Angeles based editor with over 20 years in post-production, specializing in branded content, documentary, and commercial work for some of the world's leading companies.",
    "bio2": "His work spans the full post-production pipeline—<strong>editing, color grading, and audio mixing</strong>—with fluency across <strong>Adobe Premiere, Avid and DaVinci Resolve</strong>. Recent work includes a <strong>Golden and Bronze Telly Award</strong>-winning piece for Amazon Web Services. Earlier credits include assistant editor on <em>Undefeated</em>, the <strong>2012 Academy Award winner</strong> for Best Documentary.",
